            <p>Started its journey on Instagram as a small business account. In a small business, decision-making processes are usually more streamlined, allowing for quick adaptations to market changes. We often wear many types of shirts, taking on various roles to keep the business running smoothly. This fosters a sense of ownership and dedication among team members.</p>
            <p>Bludd can leverage its existing brand identity and ethos established during its thrift account days while infusing it with a fresh streetwear vibe. This could involve maintaining a commitment to sustainability and affordability, which are often associated with thrift, while incorporating bold graphics and edgy designs characteristic of streetwear.</p>
